OL,7,FOverseas students who had their visas
OL,8,Frevoked after being wrongly accused of
OL,9,Fcheating in an English language test
OL,10,Fhave launched legal challenges against
OL,11,F, ITV News understands.
OL,13,FLaw firm Bindmans is hoping to obtain
OL,14,Fa blanket compensation scheme for 23
OL,15,Fstudents who had their visas cancelled
OL,16,Fbetween 2011 and 2014 after claims
OL,17,Fthey cheated on the test.
