OL,7,FThe students, who have already won
OL,8,Fimmigration appeals and had their
OL,9,Fvisas returned, are now seeking
OL,10,Ffinancial compensation for wrongful
OL,11,Farrest, false imprisonment, loss of
OL,12,Fearnings and damage to their mental
OL,13,Fhealth.
OL,15,FBindmans issued the claims between
OL,16,FOctober 2020 and March 2022 but only
OL,17,Fone case has settled.
