OL,7,FIt comes 10 years after the Home
OL,8,FOffice took measures to reject the
OL,9,Fvisas of an estimated 35,000
OL,10,Finternational students.
OL,12,FWhat happened in the English test
OL,13,Fscandal?
OL,15,FIn 2014, BBC Panorama broadcast
OL,16,Ffootage revealing "organised cheating"
OL,17,Fin two English language test centres
OL,18,Frun by third parties on behalf of non-
OL,19,Fprofit organisation Educational
OL,20,FTesting Service (ETS).
