OL,7,FETS used voice recognition technology
OL,8,Fto establish who had cheated by having
OL,9,Fsomeone else sit their test.
OL,11,FIt sparked a government crackdown on
OL,12,Ftest centres and after review by human
OL,13,Flisteners and other checks, ETS
OL,14,Fidentified 97% of UK tests taken
OL,15,Fbetween 2011 and 2014 as suspicious,
OL,16,Fwith 58% of 58,459 tests classified as
OL,17,F"invalid" and 39% as "questionable".
