OL,7,FThe Home Office responded by
OL,8,Finvestigating colleges, test centres
OL,9,Fand students, and began cancelling the
OL,10,Fvisas of those it considered to have
OL,11,Fcheated in the Test Of English for
OL,12,FInternational Communication (TOEIC).
OL,14,FBut a number of people caught up in
OL,15,Fthe response have protested their
OL,16,Finnocence.
