OL,7,FIn May 2019, the National Audit Office
OL,8,F(NAO) warned innocent people may have
OL,9,Fbeen removed from the UK after they
OL,10,Fwere wrongly accused of cheating in
OL,11,FEnglish language tests.
OL,13,FBut it said the Home Office's action
OL,14,Fagainst overseas students "carried
OL,15,Fwith it the possibility" that some of
OL,16,Fthose affected might have been branded
OL,17,Fcheats and removed from the UK despite
OL,18,Fbeing innocent.
