OL,7,FA Home Office spokesperson told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "The 2014 investigation into the
OL,9,Fabuse of English language testing
OL,10,Frevealed systemic cheating which was
OL,11,Findicative of significant organised
OL,12,Ffraud.
OL,14,F"The evidence provided by ETS, the
OL,15,Faction the Home Office took and the
OL,16,Fcounter arguments have all been
OL,17,Fconsidered in the series of litigation
OL,18,Fsince 2014. Courts have consistently
OL,19,Ffound the evidence was sufficient to
OL,20,Ftake the action we did.
